    <div class="container">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="sec-pill reveal">Comment √ßa marche</span>
        <h2 class="sec-title font-head reveal reveal-d1">4 √©tapes, <span class="text-teal">c'est tout</span></h2>
      </div>
